WWW::Mechanize is a Perl module for stateful programmatic web browsing, used
for automated interaction with websites.

Features include:

 * All HTTP methods
 * High-level hyperlink and HTML form support, without having to parse HTML
   yourself
 * SSL support
 * Automatic cookies
 * Custom HTTP headers
 * Automatic handling of redirections
 * Proxies
 * HTTP authentication

NOTE: If you do not have an Internet connection when building, comment
out the line 'make test' in the SlackBuild.
